##  Docker ignore rules for the server image build context.

# IDE and editor metadata
**/.classpath
**/.project
**/.settings
**/.toolstarget
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/*.*proj.user

# Source control metadata
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.dockerignore

# Build outputs and generated artifacts
**/*.dbmdl
**/*.jfm
**/bin
**/obj
**/npm-debug.log

# Frontend and package manager dependencies
**/node_modules

# Local development and deployment overrides
**/.env
**/azds.yaml
**/secrets.dev.yaml
**/values.dev.yaml

# Docker and orchestration files not needed inside the build context
**/charts
**/docker-compose*
**/Dockerfile*

# Repository documents not needed for image build
LICENSE
README.md

# Keep selected Git metadata available when needed by tooling
!**/.gitignore
!.git/HEAD
!.git/config
!.git/packed-refs
!.git/refs/heads/**
